#: ../../website/seo.rst:343
msgid "**-31** = the unique ID of the product"
msgstr ""

#: ../../website/seo.rst:345
msgid "Note that any dynamic component of an URL can be reduced to its ID. As an example, the following URLs all do a 301 redirect to the above URL:"
